13
00:03:22,285 --> 00:03:24,329
{\an8}<font color="japanese">警察の信頼を…

14
00:03:24,662 --> 00:03:26,164
{\an8}<font color="japanese">損なう事件です

15
00:03:26,247 --> 00:03:27,665
{\an8}<font color="japanese">カン容疑者は…

16
00:03:27,749 --> 00:03:29,292
{\an8}<font color="japanese">凶悪事件を解決し…

17
00:03:29,375 --> 00:03:30,501
{\an8}<font color="japanese">有能ですが…

18
00:03:30,585 --> 00:03:32,086
{\an8}<font color="japanese">功名心が強く…

19
00:03:32,170 --> 00:03:34,923
{\an8}<font color="japanese">要注意人物だった
<font color="japanese">ようです

20
00:03:35,006 --> 00:03:39,344
{\an8}<font color="japanese">鋭利な刃物で
<font color="japanese">両目を突かれたようです

21
